---
title: Miso Glazed Aubergine Tacos with Potato Wedges & Baby Gem Lettuce
description: We love good Tacos with Red onion and Sesame Mayo and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/miso-glazed-aubergine-tacos-f7ac4f95-ebe446bf.jpg
